    About

    The new Seed School was established in 2016 with Khmer as the base language and added English and Chinese in order to provide students with benefits in life and work in the future. Computer training and professional skills: which can help cultivate a sense of responsibility as well as ideas to work or choose a career in the future better.

    Vision:

    Seeing the school standing firmly and working on very well as a flagship in the country and in the world with system in order to provide the best SWIFT, and build the strongest EQUIP for the community from generation to generation so that they can be the very potential resource for the country and the glory of God.

    Mission

    1. Build a curriculum that incorporates 21st century technology.
    2. Organize the campus and the work of the academic staff as well as the healthy students who help to meet their life needs.
    3. Scientific innovation is important, not just for science subjects.
    4. Preparing students for the future is the school's plan to prepare students at all times and in all circumstances.
    5. Technology is the school's priority in integrating and educating all students and staff.

    School Website Vision:

    Turn into the digital school of the future.

    About the website

    To make it easier to read, look at the study information and create a close relationship between teachers, students and parents. The New Seed School, a staff of the Ministry of Education, Youth and Sports, created this website for the purpose of 1. Students can do research, study and self-study through many video books, textbooks that the school has posted on the website. 2. Students can read thousands of books on the school website 3. Parents of students will receive notifications through the school website.
